ificant step towards making image segmentation more\nuniversal and accessible. To support further research, we open-source our code\nand models at https://github.com/SHI-Labs/OneFormer\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Thu, 10 Nov 2022 18:56:04 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Tue, 27 Dec 2022 04:00:07 GMT"}],"update_date":"2023-01-02"}
